snippet: Osi Umenyiora of the New York Giants was fined $20,000 by the N.F.L. for missing a mandatory session with the media on Wednesday.
abstract: Osi Umenyiora of the New York Giants was fined $20,000 by the N.F.L. for missing a mandatory session with the media on Wednesday.

headline.main: Umenyiora Is Fined for Missing Media Session
headline.print_headline: N.F.L. Roundup: Umenyiora, Only Player to Miss a Mandatory Media Session, Is Fined $20,000
